        <item>
            <title>Version 2.4.0</title>
            <sparkle:releaseNotesLink>
                https://github.com/CleanClip/CleanClipApp/releases/tag/v2.4.0
            </sparkle:releaseNotesLink>
            <sparkle:releaseNotesLink xml:lang="en">
                • Now available on iOS, supporting iPhone/iPad
                • Added iCloud sync functionality for seamless data synchronization
                • Mac version users can use iOS version for free, see activation guide: ios.cleanclip.cc/activation
                • Improved Quick Menu response speed for smoother operation
                • Enhanced overall performance for better user experience
                • Fixed various known issues for improved stability
            </sparkle:releaseNotesLink>
            <sparkle:releaseNotesLink xml:lang="zh">
                • 全新推出 iOS 版本，支持在 iPhone/iPad 上使用
                • 新增 iCloud 同步功能，数据随时随地保持同步
                • Mac 版本用户可在 iOS 版本免费使用，查看激活方式：ios.cleanclip.cc/activation
                • 优化快捷菜单响应速度，操作更加流畅
                • 提升整体性能表现，使用更加顺畅
                • 修复若干已知问题，提升应用稳定性
            </sparkle:releaseNotesLink>
